properties.areaDesc: Coastal waters from High Island to Freeport TX out 20 NM; Coastal waters from Freeport to Matagorda Ship Channel TX out 20 NM
properties.headline: Dense Fog Advisory issued February 16 at 3:01PM CST until February 16 at 6:00PM CST by NWS Houston/Galveston TX
properties.description:
* WHAT...Dense fog will reduce visibility to one mile or worse.

* WHERE...Coastal waters from Freeport to Matagorda Ship Channel
TX out 20 NM and Coastal waters from High Island to Freeport
TX out 20 NM.

* WHEN...Until 6 PM CST this evening.

* IMPACTS...Low visibility will make navigation difficult.
properties.instruction:
If you must navigate, proceed with caution. Use proper fog
signals. Make sure all running lights are on. Remember to use
your radar and compass.

NWSheadline: DENSE FOG ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 6 PM CST THIS EVENING
